{"tid":1579474,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"化名: 2和B既廢青向記者解釋為何一直找不到工作 原因是他認為自己除了2手指特別靈活外並無其他個人長處","createTime":"2019-09-18T14:58:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T06:26:19.000Z","uid":44748,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"7ee9a592ef543843d6011c8d7f555a261b8c806d","tid":1579474,"uid":44748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:58:38.000Z","msg":"[本訊報] 一位記者為了解開為何一些青少年長年待在家中，並一直找不到工作的原因，於是在街中尋找一些疑似畢業過後但卻一直無所事事，並不想尋找工作的人。終於在幾經辛苦下，在街上發現一位每天下午都在街上某大快樂買飯回家，衣著不整的男子。記者上前問這位男子，得知他是已中學畢業3年並無任何工作經驗的人。他表示自己終日除了在體育台開膠post外，並不知道如何打發時間。我們的記者有嘗試過問他的名字，但他只肯透露自己的網名為: 2和B。化名2和B的他慨歎這個社會並無適合他的工作。當他被問到自己知不知道自己的長處時，他這樣回答記者:我認為自己除咗雙手2隻手指特別靈活外並無其他個人長處。而我發現咗我既中指同無名指既靈活度特別優秀。我既左手中指同無名指每分鐘可以震盪190下，而右手既中指同無名指更加可以每分鐘震盪達到200下。依家我2隻手時時刻刻都不停緊震，我相信咁樣練習法應該可以超越而家既次數。被問到這種技能對他的前途有什麼幫助，他回應沒有，說香港的工作只偏重於其他方面，沒有工作適合他這樣的人才。他又指若然香港有撩閪師的工作及需求，他早就脫離廢青這個行列。<br />\n資料來源: <img src=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jgkfmxLwnJE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjgkfmxLwnJE&h=b9b23bc6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"450ab8e5a3326619e3ff8613415f653f2bb9a434","tid":1579474,"uid":44748,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T14:59:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jgkfmxLwnJE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjgkfmxLwnJE&d=YpkAIiMN%2BbqadqYnCsWFxlEyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=3e200ce1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jgkfmxLwnJE</a>"},{"pid":"1218c577faae5527b0ba69455a100af9e7bc12bd","tid":1579474,"uid":44748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:01:03.000Z","msg":"好擔心2和B既前途<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e82f510fd2f9d8fd279b6e793e0a84ecc5097568","tid":1579474,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:02:07.000Z","msg":"Source?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e2ce14252a587e0ac37f69c5977dc8a3809fb9","tid":1579474,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:13:16.000Z","msg":"2和b 連思覺像也失調"},{"pid":"c9df7cc32cf2c99ac6f587ddd95cbb17349a864a","tid":1579474,"uid":64710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T08:18:45.000Z","msg":"2&amp;b入來未<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17acb5c26030ba8c4b0737f1b80282efeae02ddc","tid":1579474,"uid":301523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T08:35:13.000Z","msg":"其實跟番個timeline係冇問題<br />\n<br />\n九龍洌十幾拳個時和理非仲未接受到暴力.要藍絲變本加厲今日先可以私了"},{"pid":"3f01826ea5051e78c606bcd8e8daddd2fec1607e","tid":1579474,"uid":44748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T16:55:45.000Z","msg":"佢去左邊?"},{"pid":"cc0b9c29550c7b4cbfe64271e28cc7a5d0d57e55","tid":1579474,"uid":50740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T01:40:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b83027f47452d3c0128527a3f8081f5644e05cef","tid":1579474,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T02:09:17.000Z","msg":"今日專登要個90後黃絲下屬OT到9點，哈哈！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1566013\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1566013</a>"},{"pid":"73cdf83397494a10a99ef68108dd766b855028e6","tid":1579474,"uid":243550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T03:57:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d328c36c5a5e15a9dffb6b197f008c75ea481fba","tid":1579474,"uid":39912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T03:59:09.000Z","msg":"4.5cm"},{"pid":"386d226321399d09a2e37d38304c71739f4f0f4b","tid":1579474,"uid":